<p id="Par26" class="p">Our statistical model is formulated as follows for Δ
 <italic class="italic">T</italic>; an identical and independent model is used for %Δ
 <italic class="italic">P</italic>. The estimate of future change in mean temperature between 
 <italic class="italic">t</italic> = 0 and 
 <italic class="italic">t</italic> = 1, 
